The company came to an ad-based offering very late, and had to scramble to =
get it out the door, including partnering with Microsoft. That=E2=80=99s no=
t an optimal solution for the long run; Netflix needs to build its own plat=
form even as it builds up its ad-supported user base. Meanwhile, I definite=
